BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:wx36ANnHghQZI-M3sN6iH
SUMMARY:Board of Directors Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260701T101447Z
DTSTART:20260814T083000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Energy Corridor District® Board of Directors meet every sec
	ond Friday of the month at 8:30 a.m. Meetings are held at: Energy Corridor
	 District 777 North Eldridge Parkway\, Suite 270\, Houston\, Texas 77079 B
